These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: kale, pear, peas, pumpkin, zucchini, strawberry, banana
There are 7 different nationalities: colombian, thai, chinese, japanese, australian, british, indian
 1. the person eating peas is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating pumpkin is not the british##6
 3. the colombian is on the left of the person eating pear##1
 4. the indian is somewhere to the right of the australian##5
 5. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
 6. the colombian is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 7. the person eating strawberry is somewhere between the person eating pear and the thai##7
 8. the thai is on the left of the indian##1
 9. the japanese is somewhere between the person eating zucchini and the chinese##7
10. the chinese is on the left or right of the colombian##3
11. the australian is on the far left##1
12. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
13. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the right of the person eating strawberry##5
14. the person eating banana is somewhere to the right of the person eating zucchini##5
15. the person eating zucchini is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | peas    | kale    | pear | strawberry | pumpkin | zucchini    | banana |
| Nationality   | australian | colombian | chinese  | british   | japanese    | thai | indian |

