.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: eggplant, pear, orange, apricot, plum, broccoli, papaya
The people have 7 different hobbies: puzzles, board-games, baking, card-games, filmmaking, writing, video-games
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere between the person eating papaya and the person eating pear##7
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person eating apricot##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 5. the person eating eggplant is somewhere between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
 6. the person eating broccoli is somewhere between the person eating apricot and the person who's hobby is baking##7
 7. the person eating plum is somewhere between the person eating apricot and the person eating pear##7
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person eating plum##5
10. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
11. the person who's hobby is writing is not the person eating papaya##6
12. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person eating apricot##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | papaya  | orange | broccoli | apricot | eggplant     | plum | pear  |
| Hobby   | baking | writing | board-games  | video-games  | filmmaking | card-games      | puzzles |

