.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: reading, singing, writing, woodworking, magic-tricks, dancing, fishing
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: techno, disco, soul, electronic, punk, trance, salsa
 1. the fan of salsa is between the person who's hobby is writing and the fan of soul##2
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the fan of disco##5
 3. the fan of disco is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6
 4. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5
 5. the fan of techno is between the fan of trance and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
 6. the fan of soul is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
 7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 9. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere between the fan of punk and the fan of salsa##7
10. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not the fan of techno##6
13. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
14. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
15. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
16. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not the fan of trance##6
17. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
18. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
19. the fan of techno is somewhere to the left of the fan of punk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |    4    |       5       |     6     |      7      |
| Hobby         | reading | singing | dancing | magic-tricks  | writing | woodworking | fishing |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | trance       | techno   | punk | electronic           | salsa     | soul     |

