 8. the person who's sport is subwaying is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5
10. the person who's sport is rowing is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is cricket##7
