 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is not the person watching disaster movies##6
 5. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
 6. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching crime movies##5
 7. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is not the person watching crime movies##6
