11. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
12. the person watching adventure movies is the owner of the fish##1
13. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
14. the person watching spy movies is the owner of the goldfish##1
15. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
